---
title: Caribbean Beef-Pork Meatballs & Smokey Aioli with Cheesy Fries & Corn Slaw
description: Charred corn is the perfect addition to a colourful slaw, it's juicy and sweet. Keep tastiness going by spicing the beef and pork meatballs in
a Caribbean jerk seasoning. If that’s still not enough for you, we’re positive the cheesy fries will propel you to the finish line.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/glazed-caribbean-beef-pork-meatballs-1772824b.jpg
